---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Values">
  <!-- Background wrapper with image -->
  <section 
    class="relative container-x py-14 md:py-20 bg-cover bg-center" 
    style="background-image: url('/only-jesus.jpg');"
  >
    <!-- Overlay to soften the background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/85"></div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="relative text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-wide text-gray-900">
        Our Values
      </h1>

      <!-- Slogan under heading -->
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-3xl text-center text-gray-800">
        Come. See. <span class="text-[#B3282D]">Jesus</span>
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-700">
        At The Life Place, our heartbeat is Jesus.
        <p/>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-700">
          Our values shape who we are and how we live together as His people.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Values grid -->
    <div class="relative mt-12 grid gap-6 md:gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 auto-rows-fr">
      
      <!-- 1 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left gap-4">
          Hear the good news
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">Just as Jesus taught that everything in the Bible was written about Him, so every time we open the Bible, we are invited to see and meet with Him. And when we see Jesus, we hear the good news.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-gray-800">
          (Luke 24:47, John 1:19-35, 5:39, 46, 12:26-27, 13:3)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 2 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left gap-4">
          Diverse Community
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-800">
          Rooted in the good news, we celebrate every story, background, and culture—nations, tribes, peoples, and languages.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-gray-800">
          (Acts 2:46–47; Ephesians 3; Romans 8:15; Galatians 4:6; Revelation 7:9)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 3 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left gap-4">
          Extravagant Generosity
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">Made rich by what Jesus has done, we are generous and share in all things.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-gray-500">
          (Acts 2:45; 4:35; 2 Corinthians 8:2–4, 9, 16–24; 9:1–15)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 4 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left gap-4">
          Graceful Compassion
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          The good news moves us beyond our comforts to show grace to the widowed, the orphan,
          the poor, the imprisoned, and the immigrant.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-gray-500">
          (Deut 10:18; 14:29; 16:11; 24:17,19–21; Matt 25:35–36; Acts 6:1–3; Gal 2:9; James 1:27; 2:14–17; Jude 9)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 5 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left gap-4">
          Go live the story
        </h3>
        <p class=text-lg "text-gray-700">
          In our homes, workplaces, and city, we embody the good news and engage the culture with grace and courage—not to condemn, but to redeem.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-m text-center text-gray-500">
          (John 17:15–19; Acts 17:16–34; 1 Corinthians 9:19–22)
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Scripture footer -->
  <div class="border-t mt-16 pt-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <blockquote class="text-xl italic text-gray-800">
      “I came that they may have and enjoy life and have it in abundance (to the full, till it overflows)”
    </blockquote>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">John 10:10 AMP</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>